The paper deals with the aperiodic crosscorrelation of sequences, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). The use of linear recursive sequences (m-sequences) and Legendre sequences suggests a connection to discrete structures (cs.DS) and cryptography (cs.CR). The construction and analysis of sequences also involves numerical methods (cs.NA) and statistical inference (cs.SI).
